<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad"
>

<body>

<div>
  Edit branch status
</div>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/branch/@@+portlet-details" />
</metal:leftportlets>

<metal:rightportlets fill-slot="portlets_two">
</metal:rightportlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

  <div>

    <h1 tal:condition="view/label"
        tal:content="view/label">Heading from ZCML label="xxx"</h1>

    <div class="documentDescription">
      The bug branch status indicates the status of the fix for a
      particular bug in a particular branch.
    </div>

    <label>Branch</label>
    <div>
      <a href="#"
          tal:content="context/branch/displayname"
          tal:attributes="href context/branch/fmt:url">foo-bar</a>
    </div>

    <br />

    <label for="field.status">Fix Status</label>

    <form action="."
          tal:attributes="action request/URL"
          method="post"
          enctype="multipart/form-data">

    <div tal:content="structure view/status_widget" />

    <div>
      <span tal:content="context/status/description"></span>
    </div>

    <br />

    <div>
      <label for="field.whiteboard">Status Whiteboard</label>
      <div tal:content="structure view/whiteboard_widget" />
    </div>

    <div tal:condition="context/required:launchpad.Edit">
      <input type="submit" name="FORM_SUBMIT"
             value="Save Changes" />
    </div>
    <br />
    <div tal:condition="not:context/required:launchpad.Edit">
      <a href="#" tal:attributes="href context/bug/fmt:url">
        Return to bug page
      </a>
    </div>
    </form>
  </div>

</div><tal:comment condition="nothing"><!-- end main slot --></tal:comment>

<metal:block fill-slot="help">

  <p>Launchpad is integrated with the <a
    href="http://bazaar-vcs.org/">Bazaar</a> version control system. (<a
    href="http://bazaar-vcs.org/WhyUseBzr">Why use Bazaar?</a>).</p>

  <p>The status indicates the progress made on this branch to fix the bug.</p>

  <ul>
    <li><em>Fix In progress</em>: Development to fix this bug is currently
      going on in this branch.</li>

    <li><em>Fix available</em>: This branch contains a potentially useful fix
      for this bug.</li>

    <li><em>Abandoned Attempt</em>: A fix for this bug is no longer being
      worked on in this branch.</li>

    <li><em>Best Fix Available</em>: This branch contains a fix agreed upon by
      the community as being the best available branch from which to merge to
      fix this bug.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>The whiteboard is a place to write additional comments.</p>

</metal:block><tal:comment condition="nothing"><!-- end help slot --></tal:comment>

</body>
</html>
